or operator(any condition match)
db.students.find({$or:[
  {"age":{$gt:30}},
  {"age":{$lt:40}}]
});

and operator(both conditions shoud be matched here)
db.students.find({$and:[
  {"age":{$gt:30}},
  {"age":{$lt:40}}]
});

both condition shoud not match
db.students.find({$nor:[
  {"course":{$eq:"bsc"}},
  {"age":{$lt:40}}]
});

and more with update and delete functions
